{
  "title": "148862964.the Best Time To Start",
  "slug": "148862964the-best-time-to-start",
  "publishedAt": "2025-11-30T19:29:53.806Z",
  "excerpt": "...is before you need to.",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "1 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "...is before you need to.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The second best time is when it's necessary.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And the third best time is after you've stalled long enough.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Thing is, none of these options include 'when you're ready.' Because you almost never are. (Even when you say you think you are. You're not.)",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Hence the obvious workaround: if you're never going to feel like you're ready, why not default to starting before you feel like you are?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The thing about 'waiting until you're ready' is that 'ready' is",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "always",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "just another day away.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Starting now--before you're ready--is uncomfortable, but it's only way to ever to start before you need to, which is to say, the only way to ever start at all.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}